(92, 2, 87, 'History', 'History', '<p>Audacious men and women have contributed to the history of PATRIARCHE since 1780! Each of them has lent his or her personal touch to the company over the centuries. Each of them has contributed to its continuity and development. They are the foundations of PATRIARCHE&#39;s long, rich history. Today, their legacy is a guarantee of authenticity that perpetuates their legends through products that have benefited from all their know-how.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class="timeline-container" id="timeline"><!--<button class="timeline-toggle">+ Voir tous</button>-->\r\n<div class="timeline-wrapper">\r\n<h2 class="timeline-time"><span>1780</span></h2>\r\n\r\n<dl class="timeline-series">\r\n	<dt class="timeline-event" id="19540517"><a>Jean-Baptiste Patriarche</a></dt>\r\n	<dd class="timeline-event-content" id="19540517EX">\r\n	<p><img alt="" src="http://patriarche.melis.fr/assets/content/upload/images/1780(1).jpg" style="width: 248px; height: 267px; float: right;" />The origin, the founder He founded the House of PATRIARCHE P&egrave;re &amp; Fils in Beaune. He bought the Visitandines convent in Beaune (PATRIARCHE&#39;s current headquarters). He exported PATRIARCHE to Great Britain, the Netherlands and Belgium.</p>\r\n	</dd>\r\n	<!-- /.timeline-event-content -->\r\n</dl>\r\n<!-- /.timeline-series --></div>\r\n<!-- /.timeline-wrapper -->\r\n\r\n<div class="timeline-wrapper">\r\n<h2 class="timeline-time"><span>1850</span></h2>\r\n\r\n<dl class="timeline-series">\r\n	<dt class="timeline-event" id="19540517"><a>L&eacute;once Bocquet</a></dt>\r\n	<dd class="timeline-event-content" id="19550828EX">\r\n	<p><img alt="" src="http://patriarche.melis.fr/assets/content/upload/images/1850.jpg" style="width: 248px; height: 267px; float: right;" />The wine emperor...&quot; He supplied Europe&#39;s greatest courts with Burgundy wine. Confrontational and high-spirited, he was fond of luxury and gave renewed status to Ch&acirc;teau du Clos de Vougeot.</p>\r\n	</dd>\r\n	<!-- /.timeline-event-content -->\r\n</dl>\r\n<!-- /.timeline-series --></div>\r\n<!-- /.timeline-wrapper -->\r\n\r\n<div class="timeline-wrapper">\r\n<h2 class="timeline-time"><span>1880</span></h2>\r\n\r\n<dl class="timeline-series">\r\n	<dt class="timeline-event " id="19540517"><a>Pierre-Louis Perdrier</a></dt>\r\n	<dd class="timeline-event-content" id="18800904EX">\r\n	<p><img alt="" src="http://patriarche.melis.fr/assets/content/upload/images/1880.jpg" style="width: 248px; height: 267px; float: right;" />A shrewd businessman and a military hero Following a rich professional life, he teamed up with Andr&eacute; Boisseaux in the 50s with the aim of conquering new markets, including Paris, and contributed to the establishment of the PATRIARCHE P&egrave;re &amp; Fils wine merchant business.</p>\r\n	</dd>\r\n	<!-- /.timeline-event-content -->\r\n</dl>\r\n<!-- /.timeline-series --></div>\r\n<!-- /.timeline-wrapper -->\r\n\r\n<div class="timeline-wrapper">\r\n<h2 class="timeline-time"><span>1902</span></h2>\r\n\r\n<dl class="timeline-series">\r\n	<dt class="timeline-event" id="19540517"><a>No&eacute;mie Vernaux</a></dt>\r\n	<dd class="timeline-event-content" id="18800904EX">\r\n	<p><img alt="" src="http://patriarche.melis.fr/assets/content/upload/images/1902.jpg" style="width: 248px; height: 267px; float: right;" />A wine-loving woman of action A true legend who devoted her life to wine. She was the last descendant of the PATRIARCHE family. A courageous woman who was ahead of her timehe aim of conquering new markets, including Paris, and contributed to the establishment of the PATRIARCHE P&egrave;re &amp; Fils wine merchant business.</p>\r\n	</dd>\r\n	<!-- /.timeline-event-content -->\r\n</dl>\r\n<!-- /.timeline-series --></div>\r\n<!-- /.timeline-wrapper -->\r\n\r\n<div class="timeline-wrapper">\r\n<h2 class="timeline-time"><span>1940</span></h2>\r\n\r\n<dl class="timeline-series">\r\n	<dt class="timeline-event" id="19540517"><a>Andr&eacute; Boisseaux</a></dt>\r\n	<dd class="timeline-event-content" id="18800904EX">\r\n	<p><img alt="" src="http://patriarche.melis.fr/assets/content/upload/images/1940.jpg" style="width: 248px; height: 267px; float: right;" /></p>\r\n\r\n	<p>A visionary and a marketing genius&nbsp;<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	He made Patriarche one of Burgundy&#39;s leading wine houses.&nbsp;<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	The audacious creator of modern wines, an inventor of brands and of modern sponsorship.</p>\r\n\r\n	<p>.</p>\r\n	</dd>\r\n	<!-- /.timeline-event-content -->\r\n</dl>\r\n<!-- /.timeline-series --></div>\r\n<!-- /.timeline-wrapper -->\r\n\r\n<div class="timeline-wrapper">\r\n<h2 class="timeline-time"><span>1955</span></h2>\r\n\r\n<dl class="timeline-series">\r\n	<dt class="timeline-event" id="19540517"><a> Georges Kritter</a></dt>\r\n	<dd class="timeline-event-content" id="19610504EX">\r\n	<p>Il<img alt="" src="http://patriarche.melis.fr/assets/content/upload/images/1955.jpg" style="width: 248px; height: 267px; float: right;" /> He gave his name to the high-end brand of sparkling wine, KRITER. This was the beginning of a very long success story. .</p>\r\n	</dd>\r\n	<!-- /.timeline-event-content -->\r\n</dl>\r\n<!-- /.timeline-series --></div>\r\n<!-- /.timeline-wrapper -->\r\n\r\n<div class="timeline-wrapper">\r\n<h2 class="timeline-time"><span>2011</span></h2>\r\n\r\n<dl class="timeline-series">\r\n	<dt class="timeline-event" id="19630828"><a>P</a><a>ierre Castel</a></dt>\r\n	<dd class="timeline-event-content" id="19630828EX"><!-- /.media -->\r\n	<p>Patriarche moves forward as a company.&nbsp;<img alt="" src="http://patriarche.melis.fr/assets/content/upload/images/aujourdhui(1).jpg" style="width: 248px; height: 267px;" /></p>\r\n	</dd>\r\n</dl>\r\n</div>\r\n<br class="clear" />\r\n<!-- /.timeline-event-content --><!-- /.timeline-series --></div>\r\n<!-- /.timeline-wrapper --><!-- /#timelineContainer -->', 'History', 'history', 17, '1', 'assets/content/upload/slide-2.png'),
(93, 2, 87, 'Key figures', 'key figures', '<p><img alt="" src="http://patriarche.melis.fr/assets/content/upload/images/images.jpg" style="width: 299px; height: 169px; float: right;" /><strong>PATRIARCHE, a major player in the French wine industry&nbsp;with&nbsp;</strong>international representation:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>1780</strong>: PATRIARCHE was founded in Beaune. &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<strong>1904:&nbsp;</strong>the oldest vintage in our cellars&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTurnover:&nbsp;<strong>115 million Euros &nbsp;</strong> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<strong>3 million</strong>&nbsp;bottles in our cellars&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp;<br />\r\n<strong>185</strong>&nbsp;employees &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<strong>&nbsp;50,000&nbsp;visitors</strong> to our cellars each year&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>60 million&nbsp;</strong>bottles sold each year throughout the world &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <strong>1&nbsp;subsidiary</strong> in the United States&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\nAvailable in over&nbsp;<strong>85&nbsp;countries &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;5 km&nbsp;</strong>of cellars in Beaune&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'key figures', 'key-figures', 18, '1', 'assets/content/upload/slide-2.png'),
